            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$300</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ Peltier module</div></td>
            <td>Peltier (TEC) module replacement. We assess repair vs. replace economics on smaller units before ordering. Ambient temperature check included &mdash; sometimes the unit just needs a cooler location.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Fan not working</div><div class="repair-desc">Unit silent, no airflow, condensation issues</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$280</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ fan motor</div></td>
            <td>Evaporator fan or condenser fan motor replacement. Fan failure causes rapid temperature rise on both compressor and thermoelectric units.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Temperature inaccurate / fluctuating</div><div class="repair-desc">Can&rsquo;t hold set temperature, wide swings</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$160&ndash;$320</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ thermistor or thermostat</div></td>
