            <td><div class="repair-type">Excessive noise / vibration</div><div class="repair-desc">Loud compressor, rattling, vibration through floor</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$160&ndash;$340</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ compressor mounts or fan</div></td>
            <td>Compressor mounting dampers, loose internal components, fan blade contact. Vibration is a premium concern for wine storage &mdash; we address carefully.</td>
